									<% var tipArr=[{'color':'danger','info':'这份订单已经被扔进垃圾桶了'},{'color':'warning','info':'亲，不付钱可不会给你发货的哟'}
                    ,{'color':'info','info':'打包员正在玩命打包中'},{'color':'info','info':'东东已经在路上了，请准备好'}
                    ,{'color':'success','info':'所有的宝贝都已经到亲的手上'}]%>
								
										<div class="note note-<%=tipArr[order.state].color%> note-bordered">
											<p>
												 NOTE:<%=tipArr[order.state].info%>
											</p>
										</div>
									
										<div class="table-container">
										<form action="/admin/ship/create?id=<%=order.id%>" method="post">
                                            <input type="text" class="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%=_csrf%>" id="csrf" />
                                            
                                            <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover" id="datatable_shipment">
                                            <thead>
                                            <tr role="row" class="heading">
                                            <th width="1%" >
                                            <input type="checkbox" class="hidden group-checkable">
                                        </th>
                                                <th width="15%">
                                                     Shipment&nbsp;#
                                                </th>
                                                <th width="10%">
                                                     Ship&nbsp;By
                                                </th>
                                                <th width="30%">
                                                     Ship&nbsp;To
                                                </th>
                                                <th width="40%">
                                                     Shipped&nbsp;Package
                                                </th>
                                                <th width="5%">
                                                     Actions
                                                </th>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr role="row" class="filter">
                                            	<td></td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control form-filter input-sm" name="ship[shipno]">
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <select name="ship[shipby]" class="form-control form-filter input-sm">
                                                    <% var companies=[{
        "com": "顺丰",
        "no": "sf"
    },
    {
        "com": "申通",
        "no": "sto"
    },
    {
        "com": "圆通",
        "no": "yt"
    },
    {
        "com": "韵达",
        "no": "yd"
    },
    {
        "com": "天天",
        "no": "tt"
    },
    {
        "com": "EMS",
        "no": "ems"
    },
    {
        "com": "中通",
        "no": "zto"
    },
    {
        "com": "汇通",
        "no": "ht"
    },
    {
        "com": "全峰",
        "no": "qf"
    }]%>                                            
                                                    <%companies.forEach(function(company,index){%>
                                                    <option value="<%=company.no%>"><%=company.com%></option>
                                                    <%})%>
                                                    </select>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                <div class="margin-bottom-5">
                                                
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control form-filter input-sm" name="ship[shipWhere]" value="收件地址:<%=order.orderWhere%>">
                                            	</div>
                                            		                                                <div class="margin-bottom-5">
<input type="text" class="form-control input-sm" name="ship[shipWho]" value="收件人:<%=order.orderWho%>">
                                                    </div>
                                                    
                                                    <input type="text" class="form-control input-sm" name="ship[shipContact]" value="联系方式:<%=order.orderContact%>">

                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <select multiple="multiple" size="<%=details.length%>" name="dids" class="form-control form-filter input-sm">
                                                    <%details.forEach(function(detail,index){%>
                                                    <%if(detail.state==2){%>   
                                                    <option value="<%=detail.id%>"><%=detail.Item.name%>[<%=detail.Pic.picSku%>]---数量:<%=detail.amount%></option>
                                                    <%}})%>
                                                    </select>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <div class="margin-bottom-5">
                                                        <button class="btn btn-sm yellow  margin-bottom <%=(order.state == 2)?"":"disabled"%>" ><i class="fa fa-rocket"></i> 发射</button>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                                
                                            </tr>
                                            </thead>
                                            <tbody>
                                            </tbody>
                                            </table>
                                            <form>
										</div>
									</div>
									
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
